obrow traffic between popular forms and highbrow aesthetics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077357324640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773573246423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773573246/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles